author: @randyoliver7117
content: I've been a fan of hers since the beginning, and she has always struck a nerve with some people to attack her. Negative people produce negative energy. I could not imagine watching a video of a performer that I don't care for and then put the energy in to make negative comments in a happy place for the fans. What kind of person does that?
